06:03.387 --> 06:04.919
Eddie. Hey.

06:04.921 --> 06:05.854
Hey.

06:05.878 --> 06:06.656
I'm sorry I missed
you this morning.

06:06.657 --> 06:09.491
Uh, bacon, egg and cheese,
and a coffee, regular.

06:09.493 --> 06:10.759
That's what you like, right?

06:10.761 --> 06:13.662
Yes. Thank you.

06:13.664 --> 06:14.996
Oh, sorry.

06:14.998 --> 06:17.332
Uh, Josh,
this is my partner, Jamie.

06:17.334 --> 06:18.600
Jamie, this is,
uh, Josh.

06:18.602 --> 06:19.835
Nice to meet you.

06:19.837 --> 06:21.836
You're Jamie? Cool.

06:21.838 --> 06:23.938
It's good to finally
meet you, too.

06:25.375 --> 06:28.009
10-10, possible
jumper on the Queens-bound side

06:28.011 --> 06:30.511
of the Roosevelt Bridge.
Center span.

06:30.513 --> 06:32.213
Uh, 12 David responding.

06:32.215 --> 06:34.849
We got, we got to go. Sorry.

06:34.851 --> 06:36.084
Thank you.

06:36.086 --> 06:38.586
Don't forget Monday--
Bruce Springsteen.

06:39.589 --> 06:42.022
He's glad to <i>finally</i> meet me?

06:54.536 --> 06:55.936
I hate jumpers.

06:55.938 --> 06:58.005
Yeah, at
least if he jumps,

06:58.007 --> 06:59.306
it's in the East River.

06:59.308 --> 07:01.008
No splat.

07:01.010 --> 07:02.276
Exactly.

07:05.247 --> 07:07.247
I'm Jamie Reagan.
This is Eddie Janko.

07:07.249 --> 07:08.415
What's your name?

07:08.417 --> 07:10.517
Mike.

07:10.519 --> 07:11.453
Mike, what's going on,
Mike?

07:11.477 --> 07:12.653
Don't come any closer.

07:12.654 --> 07:15.388
Okay, hey... Whoa, whoa, Mike.
Hey, Mike, don't do that.

07:15.390 --> 07:17.557
Hey, I said don't come closer!
I'm not!

07:18.960 --> 07:20.460
Mike, don't do that.
I said don't come near me.

07:20.462 --> 07:22.929
Okay, I'm not.
We just want to be

07:22.931 --> 07:24.330
close enough to
hear each other.

07:25.901 --> 07:26.933
Anything?

07:26.935 --> 07:28.067
She still ain't
answering the phone.

07:28.069 --> 07:30.136
Her apartment's
around the corner.

07:30.138 --> 07:31.203
Maybe we'll get her there.

07:32.506 --> 07:34.740
Come on, move it!
Get out of the way, idiot!

07:34.742 --> 07:36.208
What's going on
over here?

07:36.210 --> 07:38.510
I don't know. Hey. Hey!

07:38.512 --> 07:40.746
Quiet down.
Come on, I got to go.

07:47.054 --> 07:49.254
Son of a bitch.

07:56.029 --> 07:57.463
Tell me you have her.

07:57.465 --> 07:58.630
Erin,

07:58.632 --> 08:00.398
good news and bad news.

08:00.400 --> 08:02.200
Good news is
we found the witness.

08:02.202 --> 08:05.136
Bad news is... she's dead.

08:10.843 --> 08:14.843
